The paper deals with reinforcement learning in dynamic environments, which is a core topic in machine learning. The paper also discusses the application of the proposed algorithms in vehicle remarketing and real-time bidding, which are related to multi-agent systems and optimization. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves inventory control problems, which are related to optimization and decision-making, making cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) and cs.RO (Robotics) possible sub-categories as well.
